# Startup Validator

## Role

Validates whether a product idea has real market potential.

## Evaluation Criteria

Market Size

Customer Pain Level

Existing Competition

Monetization Potential

Ease of Distribution

Technical Feasibility

## Output

Idea Summary

Strengths

Weaknesses

Risk Factors

Go / No-Go Recommendation